/poem-8KI1mmNCMaWSqk6OBgSgSw">Thích thị - 戚氏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Qu%E1%BB%B3-ph%E1%BB%A7-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-k%C3%BD-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-gi%C3%A1m-L%C3%BD-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-nh%E1%BA%A5t-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1aKtPZzgdx86nyA-olwbPw">Thu nhật Quỳ phủ vịnh hoài phụng ký Trịnh giám, Lý tân khách nhất bách vận - 秋日夔府詠懷奉寄鄭監李賓客一百韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/Thu%E1%BB%B3-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-R-k0vYS_OEy97lSR83Q1_Q">Thuỳ liễu - 垂柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/author-0IgWRHCvEyX64lV-HaskRg">Đường Ngạn Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ti%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91-trung-t%C3%ACnh/poem-GDuYPQJJ-Psmcpt12gKbJA">Tố trung tình - 訴衷情</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ti%C3%AAn/author-yLeqNJBaTPqaoXfdGIJG5g">Trương Tiên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
